data.description: This property is an operating AirBnB with excellent records. Springgville ranchette is a French Farmhouse Style with pool, sauna, 360 views, privacy and sits on top of a hill on over six acres. The outstanding pool and outdoor sauna are surrounded with multiple outdoor seating area, also has a little pool house. The master bedroom and  on suite bathroom with jetted tub offer a unique private haven with a balcony to enjoy your morning coffee. Vaulted ceilings in the great room open to the dining room and kitchen. The entire home has lots of oversized windows bringing the outdoors in. The huge kitchen has many upgrades including glass backsplash and a large walk in panty. The property also offer a shop/outbuilding. This home is being offered fully furnished, decorated, dishes, linens, ets.
